# Mark vendored / generated content so GitHub Linguist excludes it
# from language stats and diffs. https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist

# Vendored Microsoft Azure docs and examples shipped as a skill
skills/azure-skills/** linguist-vendored

# 3D office app assets and tests are generated/scaffolded
session-browser/claw3d/tests/** linguist-generated
session-browser/claw3d/.next/** linguist-generated

# Markdown is the primary "source" of this repo (rules, commands, skills, agents)
*.md linguist-detectable=true
